quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  4,114,"Moƴƴere alaa e ko heewi e yeewtere maɓɓe nden, si wanaa on yamirɗo sadaka, maa moƴƴere maa moƴƴiŋtingol hakkunde yimɓe ɓen. Kala waɗirɗo ɗum ɗaɓɓugol welayee Alla, arma Men Okka mo njoɓdi mawndi"
  4,115,"Kala on lunndiiɗo Nulaaɗo on ɓaawo nde paawal ngal ɓanngani mo, o jokki ko wanaa laawol gomɗimɓe ɓen, Men Hucciŋtinay mo e kon ko o hucciti, Men Naadoya mo Jahannanma, nge bonii ruttorde"
  4,116,"Pellet, Alla Yawtantaa kafidugol Mo e goɗɗum, Himo Yawtana ko jaasi ɗum wonannde on Mo O Muuyi. Kala on kafiduɗo Alla e goɗɗum, gomɗii o majjii majjere woɗɗiinde"
  4,117,"Ɓe alaa e rewude ko woori Alla, si wanaa [sanamuuji] rewɗinaaɗi, ɓe alaa e rewude si wanaa seytaane sanndalɗiinɗo"
  4,118,"Alla Huɗii ndu, ndu wi'i : \"Ma mi jogitoyo e jeyaaɓe maa ɓen geɓal farlaangal"
  4,119,"ma mi majjinoyɓe, ma mi yelinoyɓe, ma mi yamiroyɓe, ma ɓe taƴu noppi neemoraaɗi ɗin, ma mi yamirɓe, ma ɓe waylu tagu Alla ngun !\". Kala jogitiiɗo seytaane giɗo ko woori Alla, gomɗii o hayrii hayrere ɓanngunde"
  4,120,"Himo foda ɓe himo yelina ɓe, seytaane fodaali ɓe si wanaa hodo"
  4,121,"Ɓen ɗon wemoolorde maɓɓe nden ko Jahannama, ɓe heɓirtaa nge daɗirde"